1
00:00:01,836 --> 00:00:03,671
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON</i>
<i>"ENTERPRISE"...</i>

2
00:00:03,671 --> 00:00:06,423
I'M STARTING TO WONDER IF
THIS SHIP EVEN HAS LIFE SUPPORT.

3
00:00:06,423 --> 00:00:08,843
THEY MUST HAVE ATMOSPHERE
ON THEIR BRIDGE.

4
00:00:08,843 --> 00:00:12,596
THE HUMANS HAVE SEEN TOO MUCH.
WE CAN'T ALLOW THEM TO ESCAPE.

5
00:00:14,348 --> 00:00:16,642
[ BOTH GRUNT ]

6
00:00:20,855 --> 00:00:23,691
EVASIVE MANEUVERS.
GET OUR PEOPLE BACK.

7
00:00:23,691 --> 00:00:25,693
-DID WE GET EVERYONE?
-JUST THE MACOs.

8
00:00:25,693 --> 00:00:27,027
Trip, we've lost
the transporter.

9
00:00:27,027 --> 00:00:28,863
Sit tight
until we come back for you.

10
00:00:28,863 --> 00:00:29,947
UNDERSTOOD.

11
00:00:31,448 --> 00:00:33,408
IF THIS IS A ROMULAN SHIP,

12
00:00:33,408 --> 00:00:37,245
WHY WOULD THEY BE STIRRING UP
TROUBLE SO FAR FROM HOME?

13
00:00:37,245 --> 00:00:38,372
STAY OUT OF THIS, PINK-SKIN.

14
00:00:38,372 --> 00:00:39,832
SHRAN, LISTEN TO ME.

15
00:00:39,832 --> 00:00:41,709
THE SHIP THAT ATTACKED YOU
WASN'T TELLARITE.

16
00:00:41,709 --> 00:00:43,669
YOU'RE BOTH BEING SET UP.

17
00:00:43,669 --> 00:00:46,296
SOMEONE DIDN'T WANT
THIS CONFERENCE TO GO FORWARD.

18
00:00:50,634 --> 00:00:52,469
THEY'VE ENTERED THE BRIDGE.

19
00:00:52,469 --> 00:00:54,137
THERE'S NO ONE HERE.

20
00:01:01,311 --> 00:01:03,188
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

21
00:01:12,489 --> 00:01:14,992
THEY WON'T LAST MUCH LONGER.

22
00:01:14,992 --> 00:01:17,160
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

23
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:18,704
IT WILL HAVE TO WAIT.

24
00:01:18,704 --> 00:01:20,414
WE'RE APPROACHING
OUR NEXT TARGET.

25
00:01:20,414 --> 00:01:23,250
STABILIZE THE DRONE
FOR BATTLE.

26
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:26,461
ACTIVATING
THE HOLOGRAPHIC SKIN.

27
00:01:26,461 --> 00:01:29,339
USE THIS CONFIGURATION.

28
00:01:29,339 --> 00:01:31,090
YOU STILL IN ONE PIECE?

29
00:01:31,090 --> 00:01:34,302
YEAH, I'LL LET YOU KNOW
WHEN MY HEAD STOPS SPINNING.

30
00:01:34,302 --> 00:01:36,555
[ ENGINES WHOOSH ]

31
00:01:36,555 --> 00:01:38,306
FEEL THAT?

32
00:01:38,306 --> 00:01:40,308
WE'RE DROPPING OUT OF WARP.

33
00:01:40,308 --> 00:01:41,560
TARGET ACQUIRED.

34
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,520
ENGAGE VISUAL SENSORS.

35
00:01:45,981 --> 00:01:48,233
THE RIGELIANS ARE HAILING US.

36
00:01:48,233 --> 00:01:51,028
ANSWER THEM.

37
00:01:51,028 --> 00:01:53,321
-[ WEAPONS FIRE ]
-WE'RE FIRING AT SOMEONE.

38
00:01:53,321 --> 00:01:54,823
WELL, BRACE YOURSELF.

39
00:01:54,823 --> 00:01:56,909
WHOEVER IT IS,
THEY'LL BE SURE TO FIRE BACK.

40
00:01:59,286 --> 00:02:01,121
THE DRONE IS TAKING DAMAGE.

41
00:02:01,121 --> 00:02:04,583
GIVE THE RIGELIANS TIME
TO SEND THEIR DISTRESS CALL.

42
00:02:09,546 --> 00:02:13,008
NOW, DESTROY THEM.

43
00:02:23,393 --> 00:02:27,940
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG ROAD ♪

44
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:31,276
♪ GETTING FROM THERE TO HERE ♪

45
00:02:31,276 --> 00:02:35,072
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME ♪

46
00:02:35,072 --> 00:02:38,700
♪ BUT MY TIME IS FINALLY NEAR ♪

47
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:43,330
♪ AND I WILL SEE MY DREAM
COME ALIVE AT LAST ♪

48
00:02:43,330 --> 00:02:46,834
♪ I WILL TOUCH THE SKY ♪

49
00:02:46,834 --> 00:02:50,754
♪ AND THEY'RE NOT GONNA
HOLD ME DOWN NO MORE ♪

50
00:02:50,754 --> 00:02:53,381
♪ NO, THEY'RE NOT GONNA
CHANGE MY MIND ♪

51
00:02:53,381 --> 00:02:56,510
♪ 'CAUSE I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

52
00:02:56,510 --> 00:02:58,553
♪ OF THE HEART ♪

53
00:02:58,553 --> 00:03:01,640
♪ I'M GOING WHERE MY HEART
WILL TAKE ME ♪

54
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:06,561
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH TO BELIEVE ♪

55
00:03:06,561 --> 00:03:09,564
♪ I CAN DO ANYTHING ♪

56
00:03:09,564 --> 00:03:13,360
♪ I'VE GOT STRENGTH
OF THE SOUL ♪

57
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:16,989
♪ AND NO ONE'S GONNA BEND
OR BREAK ME ♪

58
00:03:16,989 --> 00:03:22,661
♪ I CAN REACH ANY STAR ♪

59
00:03:22,661 --> 00:03:24,496
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

60
00:03:24,496 --> 00:03:26,581
♪ I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT ♪

61
00:03:26,581 --> 00:03:30,502
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

62
00:03:30,502 --> 00:03:35,298
♪ FAITH OF THE HEART ♪

63
00:03:42,556 --> 00:03:45,017
CAPTAIN'S STARLOG,
SUPPLEMENTAL.

64
00:03:45,017 --> 00:03:47,310
FOR NOW, THE TRUCE
BETWEEN THE ANDORIANS

65
00:03:47,310 --> 00:03:49,938
AND TELLARITES
ON<i> ENTERPRISE</i> IS HOLDING.

66
00:03:49,938 --> 00:03:53,692
BUT STARFLEET HAS INFORMED ME
OF A NEW DIPLOMATIC CRISIS.

67
00:03:53,692 --> 00:03:57,529
IT WAS A HEAVILY ARMED
SCOUT SHIP WITH A CREW OF 17.

68
00:03:57,529 --> 00:03:59,781
THERE WERE NO SURVIVORS.

69
00:03:59,781 --> 00:04:01,533
WHY DOES STARFLEET THINK

70
00:04:01,533 --> 00:04:03,827
THIS IS CONNECTED
TO THE OTHER INCIDENTS?

71
00:04:03,827 --> 00:04:05,913
RIGELIANS TRANSMITTED
A VISUAL RECORD

72
00:04:05,913 --> 00:04:08,082
OF THE SHIP
THAT ATTACKED THEM.

73
00:04:08,082 --> 00:04:09,791
I'M TOLD
THEIR TRADE COMMISSION

74
00:04:09,791 --> 00:04:13,670
IS DEMANDING COMPENSATION
AND MY ARREST.

75
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:18,050
WHOEVER'S BEHIND
THESE ATTACKS,

76
00:04:18,050 --> 00:04:19,676
THEY'RE TRYING TO DO
MORE THAN PROVOKE

77
00:04:19,676 --> 00:04:22,804
A WAR BETWEEN
ANDORIANS AND TELLARITES.

78
00:04:22,804 --> 00:04:27,475
THIS IS AN ATTEMPT TO
DESTABILIZE THE ENTIRE REGION.

79
00:04:27,475 --> 00:04:31,312
WE NEED TO FIND THE MARAUDER
BEFORE IT ATTACKS AGAIN.

80
00:04:31,312 --> 00:04:33,941
I'VE FOUND A WAY TO DETECT
THEIR WARP SIGNATURE.

81
00:04:33,941 --> 00:04:35,817
AND TRAVIS
DESIGNED A SENSOR GRID

82
00:04:35,817 --> 00:04:38,278
THAT SHOULD EXTEND OUR RANGE.

83
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:40,197
HOW MANY SHIPS WILL IT TAKE
TO MAKE THIS WORK?

84
00:04:40,197 --> 00:04:42,282
ONLY 128.

85
00:04:46,536 --> 00:04:49,748
THERE'S JUST ONE WAY WE CAN GET
THAT MANY SHIPS TO HELP US.

86
00:04:57,297 --> 00:04:58,673
TALAS.

87
00:05:01,885 --> 00:05:04,596
HAVE YOU COME
TO TAKE ME HOME?

88
00:05:04,596 --> 00:05:07,766
I THINK THIS DENOBULAN DOCTOR

89
00:05:07,766 --> 00:05:10,060
IS SECRETLY IN LOVE WITH YOU.

90
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:12,687
HE WANTS TO KEEP YOU TO HIMSELF.

91
00:05:14,606 --> 00:05:18,485
YOU SAID MY WOUND
WAS SUPERFICIAL.

92
00:05:18,485 --> 00:05:21,989
YOU WERE ONLY GRAZED,

93
00:05:21,989 --> 00:05:24,658
BUT THE PHASE PISTOL
WAS SET TO KILL.

94
00:05:24,658 --> 00:05:27,661
THAT TELLARITE PIG.

95
00:05:27,661 --> 00:05:30,247
IS THERE ANY OTHER KIND?

96
00:05:30,247 --> 00:05:34,168
I'VE SEEN WHAT PHASE-PULSE
INFECTION CAN DO TO ANDORIANS.

97
00:05:34,168 --> 00:05:37,963
YOU'RE GOING TO BE FINE.

98
00:05:37,963 --> 00:05:42,676
WE'LL BE HOME SOON,
THE TWO OF US.

99
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,307
DON'T LET ME DIE UNAVENGED.

100
00:05:50,433 --> 00:05:52,477
I WON'T.

101
00:05:55,730 --> 00:05:58,692
I'M SORRY. SHE NEEDS TO REST.

102
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:02,196
YOU SEE WHAT I MEAN?

103
00:06:02,196 --> 00:06:04,489
HE CAN'T GET ENOUGH OF YOU.

104
00:06:07,617 --> 00:06:09,911
I'M JEALOUS.

105
00:06:18,837 --> 00:06:20,797
DOCTOR.

106
00:06:32,433 --> 00:06:33,601
HOW IS SHE?

107
00:06:33,601 --> 00:06:35,270
LUCKY TO BE ALIVE.

108
00:06:38,648 --> 00:06:41,109
I HAVE A PROPOSAL.

109
00:06:41,109 --> 00:06:44,946
IF IT INVOLVES KILLING
TELLARITES, I'M ALL FOR IT.

110
00:06:53,372 --> 00:06:55,790
YOUR SHIP IS ADRIFT
IN ENEMY SPACE,

111
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:57,834
DAMAGED AND DEFENSELESS,

112
00:06:57,834 --> 00:07:01,420
BECAUSE OF A SINGLE
RIGELIAN SCOUT SHIP?

113
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:04,758
IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT ME
TO REPORT TO THE SENATE?

114
00:07:04,758 --> 00:07:06,676
THE DRONE
HAS TAKEN DAMAGE BEFORE.

115
00:07:06,676 --> 00:07:08,803
IT'S DESIGNED TO SELF-REPAIR.

116
00:07:08,803 --> 00:07:11,181
IF OUR ENEMIES FIND IT --

117
00:07:11,181 --> 00:07:13,267
THAT'S THE POINT
OF THIS PROJECT.

118
00:07:13,267 --> 00:07:16,270
NO PRISONERS TO CAPTURE,
NO BODIES TO RECOVER.

119
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:20,565
THESE DRONE SHIPS CAN NEVER
BE TRACED BACK TO US.

120
00:07:20,565 --> 00:07:22,734
THIS PROTOTYPE'S
A MODIFIED WARBIRD.

121
00:07:22,734 --> 00:07:24,444
THE VULCANS WOULD IDENTIFY IT

122
00:07:24,444 --> 00:07:26,696
THE MOMENT THEY INSPECTED
THE PROPULSION MATRIX.

123
00:07:26,696 --> 00:07:29,908
THE VULCANS WON'T
GET ANYWHERE NEAR IT.

124
00:07:29,908 --> 00:07:33,870
DON'T UNDERESTIMATE
OUR DISTANT BROTHERS.

125
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:35,622
BRING YOUR SHIP HOME.

126
00:07:35,622 --> 00:07:38,583
I'LL TELL THE SENATE THAT
YOUR TEST HAS BEEN A SUCCESS.

127
00:07:38,583 --> 00:07:43,171
OTHERWISE, THEY'LL MAKE SOMEONE
PAY FOR THIS FAILURE.

128
00:07:49,136 --> 00:07:53,556
AND I PROMISE YOU,
IT WON'T BE ME.

129
00:07:53,556 --> 00:07:56,059
JOLAN TRU, ADMIRAL.

130
00:08:03,608 --> 00:08:04,692
[ DOOR CHIMES ]

131
00:08:04,692 --> 00:08:05,860
COME IN.

132
00:08:07,237 --> 00:08:08,989
ADMIRAL GARDNER JUST CALLED.

133
00:08:08,989 --> 00:08:11,532
HE'S SENDING EVERY SHIP
AVAILABLE, BUT AT TOP SPEED,

134
00:08:11,532 --> 00:08:13,994
IT'LL TAKE WEEKS
FOR MOST OF THEM TO GET HERE.

135
00:08:13,994 --> 00:08:15,412
WHAT ABOUT<i> COLUMBIA?</i>

136
00:08:15,412 --> 00:08:17,705
SHE'S STUCK IN DRY DOCK --
ENGINE TROUBLE.

137
00:08:17,705 --> 00:08:19,499
DID YOU GET THROUGH
TO YOUR PEOPLE?

138
00:08:19,499 --> 00:08:22,836
MINISTER T'PAU IS
DISPATCHING 23 VESSELS.

139
00:08:22,836 --> 00:08:24,421
THAT'S ALL?

140
00:08:24,421 --> 00:08:26,340
THE HIGH COMMAND
HAS BEEN DISBANDED.

141
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:29,176
MANY OF OUR SHIPS NO LONGER
HAVE FULL CREW COMPLEMENTS.

142
00:08:29,176 --> 00:08:32,929
T'PAU COULD HAVE PICKED
A BETTER TIME TO CLEAN HOUSE.

143
00:08:32,929 --> 00:08:35,765
ANDORIAN AND TELLARITE
FLEET DEPLOYMENTS?

144
00:08:35,765 --> 00:08:38,059
I'M THINKING OF ASKING THEM
TO JOIN US.

145
00:08:39,769 --> 00:08:42,772
WITHOUT MORE SHIPS, OUR SENSOR
NET'S GONNA HAVE A GAPING HOLE.

146
00:08:42,772 --> 00:08:45,608
THE MARAUDER COULD FLY RIGHT
THROUGH IT, AND WE'D NEVER KNOW.

147
00:08:45,608 --> 00:08:47,902
HAVE YOU DISCUSSED THIS
WITH COMMANDER SHRAN

148
00:08:47,902 --> 00:08:49,529
OR AMBASSADOR GRAL?

149
00:08:49,529 --> 00:08:51,365
NOT YET.

150
00:08:51,365 --> 00:08:53,908
EVEN IF BOTH SIDES WERE TO
AGREE, WHICH SEEMS UNLIKELY,

151
00:08:53,908 --> 00:08:56,619
THEIR DEPLOYMENTS
WOULD HAVE TO BE COORDINATED,

152
00:08:56,619 --> 00:08:58,372
A COMMAND HIERARCHY
ESTABLISHED.

153
00:08:58,372 --> 00:09:00,081
AN ANDORIAN CAPTAIN
MIGHT HAVE A PROBLEM

154
00:09:00,081 --> 00:09:02,709
-TAKING ORDERS FROM
A TELLARITE?
-PRECISELY.

155
00:09:02,709 --> 00:09:04,794
THERE'S ONE SPECIES

156
00:09:04,794 --> 00:09:08,465
THAT'S ON FRIENDLY TERMS
WITH BOTH OF THEM -- HUMANS.

157
00:09:08,465 --> 00:09:12,719
<i>ENTERPRISE</i> COULD SERVE
AS THE COMMAND SHIP,

158
00:09:12,719 --> 00:09:14,471
RELAYING ALL ORDERS.

159
00:09:14,471 --> 00:09:16,806
THE OTHER SHIPS
WOULD ONLY HAVE

160
00:09:16,806 --> 00:09:18,641
TO EXCHANGE
COMMUNICATION CODES.

161
00:09:18,641 --> 00:09:20,352
IT<i> MIGHT</i> WORK.

162
00:09:20,352 --> 00:09:22,270
YOU DON'T SOUND
TOO OPTIMISTIC.

163
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:25,273
THESE FOUR SPECIES HAVE NEVER
COOPERATED ON A MUTUAL ENDEAVOR.

164
00:09:25,273 --> 00:09:26,816
AS FAR AS I KNOW,

165
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:29,236
NO ONE'S EVER TRIED
TO GET THEM TOGETHER BEFORE.

166
00:09:29,236 --> 00:09:32,989
FROM WHAT I'VE HEARD ABOUT THESE
ROMULANS, THEY MEAN BUSINESS.

167
00:09:32,989 --> 00:09:34,741
IF THEY'RE BEHIND THESE ATTACKS,

168
00:09:34,741 --> 00:09:36,910
WE HAVE TO FIND SOME WAY
TO STOP THEM,

169
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,745
OR NEXT TIME,

170
00:09:38,745 --> 00:09:42,707
THEY MIGHT COME BACK
WITH A THOUSAND OF THOSE SHIPS.

171
00:09:42,707 --> 00:09:45,085
SOME OF THESE CIRCUITS
ARE LIVE,

172
00:09:45,085 --> 00:09:47,379
BUT I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THEY'RE FOR.

173
00:09:47,379 --> 00:09:50,090
I CAN'T FIGURE OUT
WHAT HALF THIS STUFF IS.

174
00:09:50,090 --> 00:09:52,259
WHAT ABOUT THE OTHER HALF?

175
00:09:52,259 --> 00:09:54,802
WELL, I THINK I FOUND
AN ENVIRONMENTAL SYSTEM.

176
00:09:54,802 --> 00:09:56,430
THAT'D MAKE SENSE.

177
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:58,723
THESE CONSOLES LOOK
LIKE CREW STATIONS.

178
00:09:58,723 --> 00:10:00,308
HERE GOES.

179
00:10:03,895 --> 00:10:07,774
WELL, HOW ABOUT THAT?

180
00:10:07,774 --> 00:10:10,485
IN A FEW MINUTES,
WE'LL HAVE HEAT AND AIR.

181
00:10:10,485 --> 00:10:12,695
AH.

182
00:10:12,695 --> 00:10:16,324
DO YOU THINK IT'S POSSIBLE THAT
THERE'S NO ONE ELSE ONBOARD?

183
00:10:16,324 --> 00:10:18,452
WHY WOULD A ROBOT SHIP
HAVE A BRIDGE LIKE THIS?

184
00:10:18,452 --> 00:10:20,828
IT COULD BE A PROTOTYPE --

185
00:10:20,828 --> 00:10:23,623
OUTFIT AN EXISTING SHIP WITH
THE LATEST IN COMPUTER CONTROLS.

186
00:10:23,623 --> 00:10:26,418
WELL, THAT'D MAKE THINGS
A WHOLE LOT EASIER FOR US.

187
00:10:26,418 --> 00:10:27,919
HOW'S THAT?

188
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:29,629
IF THIS SHIP'S RUN BY COMPUTER,

189
00:10:29,629 --> 00:10:31,965
WHAT WE NEED TO DO IS
FIND THE OFF SWITCH.

190
00:10:31,965 --> 00:10:34,593
AH.

191
00:10:34,593 --> 00:10:37,804
I'D RATHER COHABIT
WITH KLINGON TARGS

192
00:10:37,804 --> 00:10:39,973
THAN JOIN FORCES
WITH TELLARITES!

193
00:10:39,973 --> 00:10:43,935
YOUR PERSONAL MATING PREFERENCE
IS NO CONCERN OF MINE.

194
00:10:50,275 --> 00:10:53,778
IF YOU'RE WAITING FOR ME
TO STOP YOU, DON'T WORRY.

195
00:10:53,778 --> 00:10:54,946
I WON'T.

196
00:10:54,946 --> 00:10:56,197
YOU HEARD WHAT HE SAID!

197
00:10:56,197 --> 00:10:58,575
AND I HEARD WHAT YOU SAID.

198
00:10:58,575 --> 00:11:01,744
SO NOW IT'S TIME FOR BOTH
OF YOU TO LISTEN TO ME.

199
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:09,085
INSTEAD OF INSULTING YOU
TO MAKE YOU FEEL AT HOME

200
00:11:09,085 --> 00:11:11,129
AND PUTTING UP
WITH YOUR ARROGANCE

201
00:11:11,129 --> 00:11:13,632
AS A SIGN OF MY RESPECT,
WHY DON'T THE TWO OF YOU TRY

202
00:11:13,632 --> 00:11:15,967
BEHAVING LIKE HUMANS
FOR A CHANGE?

203
00:11:15,967 --> 00:11:18,094
AND YOU SAID YOU WOULDN'T
BE INSULTING?

204
00:11:27,270 --> 00:11:29,397
THERE'S ONE THING
HUMANS SEEM TO DO BETTER

205
00:11:29,397 --> 00:11:31,732
THAN ANY SPECIES WE'VE MET.

206
00:11:31,732 --> 00:11:35,236
WHEN WE'RE FACED
WITH A COMMON THREAT,

207
00:11:35,236 --> 00:11:39,907
WE PUT OUR DIFFERENCES ASIDE
AND TRY TO COOPERATE.

208
00:11:42,827 --> 00:11:47,165
SOMEONE IS DETERMINED TO START
A WAR IN THIS REGION.

209
00:11:47,165 --> 00:11:49,876
I'VE SHOWN YOU
HOW WE CAN STOP THEM.

210
00:11:49,876 --> 00:11:51,710
BUT IF YOU DON'T
UNDERSTAND THAT,

211
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:53,921
FEEL FREE TO STRANGLE
EACH OTHER.

212
00:11:55,006 --> 00:11:56,757
JUST REMEMBER,

213
00:11:56,757 --> 00:12:01,471
THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT
THIS MARAUDER WANTS YOU TO DO.

214
00:12:11,439 --> 00:12:12,857
WE'VE GONE BACK TO WARP.

215
00:12:12,857 --> 00:12:14,025
AND JUST WHEN IT HAPPENED,
I GOT A POWER SPIKE

216
00:12:14,025 --> 00:12:15,485
FROM ONE OF THESE CONDUITS.

217
00:12:15,485 --> 00:12:17,612
DO YOU THINK WARP CONTROL
RUNS THROUGH HERE?

218
00:12:17,612 --> 00:12:19,614
IF THIS SHIP WAS
ORIGINALLY BUILT FOR A CREW,

219
00:12:19,614 --> 00:12:22,909
ALL OF ITS CONTROLS
SHOULD CONNECT TO THE BRIDGE.

220
00:12:22,909 --> 00:12:24,285
MAYBE THEY NEVER
GOT DISCONNECTED.

221
00:12:24,285 --> 00:12:26,705
KEEP YOUR EYES
ON THESE CONSOLES.

222
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:32,377
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

223
00:12:35,088 --> 00:12:36,256
DID YOU DO THAT?

224
00:12:39,092 --> 00:12:41,261
EVEN MONEY WE JUST FOUND
THE PROPULSION CONTROLS.

225
00:12:41,261 --> 00:12:42,929
WHAT ARE THEY DOING?

226
00:12:42,929 --> 00:12:44,931
I CAN'T TELL FOR SURE.
VISUAL SURVEILLANCE IS OFFLINE.

227
00:12:44,931 --> 00:12:46,349
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

228
00:12:46,349 --> 00:12:48,101
THE DRONE IS
DROPPING OUT OF WARP.

229
00:12:48,101 --> 00:12:49,810
[ ENGINE WHOOSHES ]

230
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:51,770
YOU FOUND THE OFF SWITCH?

231
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:53,981
ALL I DID WAS INTERRUPT
THE POWER TO THE WARP CONTROLS.

232
00:12:53,981 --> 00:12:57,026
THERE'S PROBABLY A BACKUP THAT
WILL SWITCH ON IN A FEW MINUTES.

233
00:12:57,026 --> 00:12:59,487
CAN YOU MAKE
ANY SENSE OF THIS?

234
00:13:01,406 --> 00:13:03,533
AH, WHERE'S HOSHI
WHEN YOU NEED HER?

235
00:13:05,034 --> 00:13:07,662
THAT'S WHERE WE ARE.

236
00:13:09,372 --> 00:13:12,459
I'M GONNA GUESS THAT'S THE POWER
CIRCUIT I JUST SHUT DOWN.

237
00:13:12,459 --> 00:13:14,461
IF THIS WERE<i> ENTERPRISE,</i>

238
00:13:14,461 --> 00:13:17,255
THAT'D BE THE POWER COUPLING FOR
THE ENTIRE WARP-CONTROL SYSTEM,

239
00:13:17,255 --> 00:13:19,090
INCLUDING THE BACKUPS.

240
00:13:23,094 --> 00:13:25,513
SHOULD BE RIGHT THROUGH THERE.

241
00:13:28,015 --> 00:13:30,477
HUH. MAESTRO.

242
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,982
ONE OF THEM'S LEFT THE BRIDGE.
HE'S IN THE SERVICE JUNCTION.

243
00:13:35,982 --> 00:13:37,858
WHY?

244
00:13:37,858 --> 00:13:40,987
IT APPEARS HE'S LOCATED THE MAIN
COUPLING FOR THE WARP MATRIX.

245
00:13:40,987 --> 00:13:42,614
WHAT ELSE IS IN THERE?

246
00:13:46,117 --> 00:13:48,827
JUST WHAT WE NEED TO KILL HIM.

247
00:13:50,829 --> 00:13:53,792
OKAY, MALCOLM.
I'M GONNA FLIP THROUGH THESE,
LIKE, CIRCUIT BREAKERS.

248
00:13:53,792 --> 00:13:56,503
LET ME KNOW
HOW THE DIAGRAM CHANGES.

249
00:13:56,503 --> 00:13:57,836
READY WHEN YOU ARE.

250
00:13:57,836 --> 00:13:59,255
THERE'S THE FIRST ONE.

251
00:14:01,048 --> 00:14:03,593
-IT WENT OUT.
-HE'S DISABLING
THE WARP SYSTEM.

252
00:14:03,593 --> 00:14:05,553
IS SELF-REPAIR
STILL ACTIVATED?

253
00:14:05,553 --> 00:14:07,639
IT'LL TAKE MORE THAN A DAY
TO REROUTE THE MAJOR CIRCUITS.

254
00:14:07,639 --> 00:14:09,516
WE DON'T HAVE A DAY.

255
00:14:09,516 --> 00:14:13,645
ONE OF THEM IS STILL
IN THE SERVICE JUNCTION.

256
00:14:13,645 --> 00:14:15,355
SEAL HIM IN.

257
00:14:15,355 --> 00:14:17,273
I'M GONNA SEE IF THERE'S
A COMMUNICATIONS CIRCUIT

258
00:14:17,273 --> 00:14:19,192
WE CAN TAP INTO.

259
00:14:19,192 --> 00:14:20,860
MALCOLM!

260
00:14:22,111 --> 00:14:23,196
[ COMMUNICATOR BEEPS ]

261
00:14:23,196 --> 00:14:24,905
MALCOLM,
DID YOU TOUCH SOMETHING?

262
00:14:24,905 --> 00:14:26,907
WASN'T ME.

263
00:14:34,248 --> 00:14:36,250
DO THE HATCH CONTROLS
WORK ON YOUR SIDE?

264
00:14:36,250 --> 00:14:39,128
NEGATIVE.
THEY'RE NOT RESPONDING.

265
00:14:39,128 --> 00:14:42,256
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

266
00:14:42,256 --> 00:14:45,802
Listen carefully,
and you won't be harmed.

267
00:14:45,802 --> 00:14:48,346
-WHO ARE YOU?
-I CONTROL THE SHIP.

268
00:14:48,346 --> 00:14:50,139
NOT ANYMORE, YOU DON'T.

269
00:14:55,102 --> 00:14:57,480
COMMANDER, WHAT'S HAPPENING?

270
00:14:58,981 --> 00:15:00,734
REACTOR COOLANT.

271
00:15:00,734 --> 00:15:02,902
RADIATION'S AT 100 ROENTGENS
AND CLIMBING.

272
00:15:02,902 --> 00:15:05,363
That gives you seven minutes,
Commander.

273
00:15:05,363 --> 00:15:08,783
Reestablish the warp matrix,
or you will die.

274
00:15:16,666 --> 00:15:19,168
COMPLIMENTS
OF THE IMPERIAL GUARD.

275
00:15:19,168 --> 00:15:20,628
THESE ARE
THE COMMUNICATION CODES

276
00:15:20,628 --> 00:15:22,839
WE'LL USE FOR
THE JOINT OPERATION.

277
00:15:22,839 --> 00:15:27,051
GRAL'S INFORMED ME THAT THE
TELLARITES ARE ALSO TAKING PART.

278
00:15:27,051 --> 00:15:29,512
SO THEY'LL NEED
THESE CODES AS WELL.

279
00:15:29,512 --> 00:15:32,724
DO WHAT YOU HAVE TO.

280
00:15:32,724 --> 00:15:34,684
I APPRECIATE YOUR COOPERATION.

281
00:15:34,684 --> 00:15:37,437
YOU'RE NOT ESPECIALLY DIFFICULT
TO WORK WITH, CAPTAIN.

282
00:15:37,437 --> 00:15:38,897
UNLIKE TELLARITES,

283
00:15:38,897 --> 00:15:41,107
YOU UNDERSTAND ETHICS
AND TRY TO LIVE BY THEM.

284
00:15:41,107 --> 00:15:42,650
TRY?

285
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:45,486
WELL, NOBODY'S PERFECT.

286
00:15:45,486 --> 00:15:48,114
HAVE YOU SERVED ON
ALL THESE VESSELS?

287
00:15:48,114 --> 00:15:52,535
A FEW OF THEM ARE
A BIT BEFORE MY TIME.

288
00:15:52,535 --> 00:15:54,454
BUT THEY WERE ALL
NAMED<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

289
00:15:54,454 --> 00:15:58,625
THIS ONE SAILED EARTH'S OCEANS
ALMOST 400 YEARS AGO.

290
00:15:58,625 --> 00:16:01,795
MY VESSEL, THE<i> KUMARI,</i>
WAS NAMED

291
00:16:01,795 --> 00:16:06,132
FOR THE FIRST ICE-CUTTER
TO CIRCUMNAVIGATE ANDORIA.

292
00:16:06,132 --> 00:16:10,595
PERHAPS FUTURE SHIPS WILL
BE NAMED AFTER OUR VESSELS,

293
00:16:10,595 --> 00:16:15,266
ESPECIALLY IF WE DO
SOMETHING HISTORIC TOGETHER.

294
00:16:15,266 --> 00:16:19,061
THERE'S NO REASON OUR PEOPLE
CAN'T BECOME ALLIES.

295
00:16:22,064 --> 00:16:24,776
AGREED.

296
00:16:24,776 --> 00:16:26,444
PAY ATTENTION
TO THAT BOARD, MALCOLM.

297
00:16:26,444 --> 00:16:28,613
I'M GONNA TRY TO CUT POWER
TO THE REACTOR.

298
00:16:28,613 --> 00:16:31,866
I'VE GOT A BETTER IDEA.
MAKE SURE YOU'RE WELL AWAY
FROM THE DOOR.

299
00:16:31,866 --> 00:16:33,618
YOU'RE WASTING TIME, COMMANDER.

300
00:16:33,618 --> 00:16:36,245
THE RADIATION WILL BE FATAL
IN THREE MINUTES.

301
00:16:36,245 --> 00:16:38,247
I can save you.

302
00:16:45,379 --> 00:16:47,340
MALCOLM,
WHAT HAPPENED TO THE BOARD?

303
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:48,591
EVERYTHING'S OFF.

304
00:16:48,591 --> 00:16:52,052
THAT'S MORE LIKE IT.

305
00:16:52,052 --> 00:16:53,429
RADIATION'S FALLING.

306
00:16:53,429 --> 00:16:55,222
THEY'VE TAKEN
THE REACTOR OFFLINE.

307
00:16:55,222 --> 00:16:57,016
ACTIVATE THE BACKUP SEQUENCER.

308
00:17:01,312 --> 00:17:03,564
I'm still in control.

309
00:17:03,564 --> 00:17:05,942
There's nothing you can do
to save your life

310
00:17:05,942 --> 00:17:08,903
EXCEPT FOLLOW MY INSTRUCTIONS.

311
00:17:08,903 --> 00:17:10,905
WE'VE RECEIVED
THE FINAL CONFIRMATIONS.

312
00:17:10,905 --> 00:17:13,867
ALL 128 SHIPS ARE IN POSITION.

313
00:17:13,867 --> 00:17:16,285
-[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]
-Phlox to Captain Archer.

314
00:17:16,285 --> 00:17:17,829
GO AHEAD.

315
00:17:17,829 --> 00:17:20,623
I require you in sick bay
as soon as possible.

316
00:17:31,843 --> 00:17:34,554
NO.

317
00:17:34,554 --> 00:17:36,389
I DID EVERYTHING I COULD.

318
00:17:38,307 --> 00:17:42,228
YOU SAID SHE'D RECOVER.

319
00:17:42,228 --> 00:17:43,730
SHRAN.

320
00:17:49,402 --> 00:17:52,071
[ SIGHS ]

321
00:18:00,496 --> 00:18:03,041
[ SOBBING ]

322
00:18:05,251 --> 00:18:06,586
NO.

323
00:18:15,053 --> 00:18:16,345
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

324
00:18:16,345 --> 00:18:19,265
Commander, what's your status?

325
00:18:19,265 --> 00:18:20,850
I SHOULD HAVE BROUGHT MY HELMET.

326
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:23,269
RADIATION'S AT 180 AND CLIMBING.

327
00:18:23,269 --> 00:18:24,562
I CAN'T SHUT IT DOWN.

328
00:18:24,562 --> 00:18:26,188
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO DIE LIKE THIS.

329
00:18:26,188 --> 00:18:27,774
YOU'RE NOT GETTING
THIS SHIP BACK.

330
00:18:27,774 --> 00:18:29,233
You're wrong, Commander.

331
00:18:29,233 --> 00:18:31,402
EVENTUALLY
IT WILL REPAIR ITSELF.

332
00:18:31,402 --> 00:18:33,529
YOU'LL HAVE DIED FOR NOTHING.

333
00:18:33,529 --> 00:18:36,657
ALL RIGHT.
I'LL RECONNECT THE MATRIX.

334
00:18:36,657 --> 00:18:37,951
OPEN THE HATCH!

335
00:18:37,951 --> 00:18:41,287
MALCOLM, NO!

336
00:18:41,287 --> 00:18:42,538
THAT'S AN ORDER!

337
00:18:42,538 --> 00:18:43,831
[ PANTING ]

338
00:18:48,044 --> 00:18:49,211
COMMANDER?

339
00:18:49,211 --> 00:18:50,337
Do your duty, Malcolm.

340
00:18:50,337 --> 00:18:52,423
RESTORE THE MATRIX.

341
00:18:52,423 --> 00:18:54,300
SAVE YOUR COMMANDER'S LIFE.

342
00:19:01,348 --> 00:19:04,518
THERE! EVERY TELLARITE SHIP IS
CONNECTED TO YOUR SENSOR NETWORK

343
00:19:04,518 --> 00:19:07,354
DESPITE THE INEFFICIENT
ANDORIAN CODES.

344
00:19:08,731 --> 00:19:10,733
NOW COMES THE HARD PART.

345
00:19:10,733 --> 00:19:13,444
WE HAVE TO SIT AND WAIT.

346
00:19:13,444 --> 00:19:15,321
WE'RE NOT A PATIENT PEOPLE.

347
00:19:15,321 --> 00:19:17,364
I'VE NOTICED.

348
00:19:17,364 --> 00:19:18,950
-MAYBE THAT'S
SOMETHING WE CAN --
-[ DOOR OPENS ]

349
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:21,577
I ONLY WANT TO TALK TO HIM!

350
00:19:31,545 --> 00:19:33,255
I ONLY WANT TO TALK.

351
00:19:40,387 --> 00:19:41,764
WE'RE LISTENING.

352
00:19:52,358 --> 00:19:56,445
YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT TALAS,

353
00:19:56,445 --> 00:19:58,405
THE WOMAN YOU KILLED.

354
00:19:58,405 --> 00:19:59,991
SHE ATTACKED US.

355
00:19:59,991 --> 00:20:03,410
THE ATTACK WAS OVER
WHEN YOU SHOT HER.

356
00:20:03,410 --> 00:20:05,538
BUT I'M NOT HERE
TO ARGUE THAT.

357
00:20:05,538 --> 00:20:08,415
HER FAMILY WAS PRIVILEGED,

358
00:20:08,415 --> 00:20:11,085
HER PARENTS WEALTHY.

359
00:20:11,085 --> 00:20:13,754
SHE COULD HAVE CHOSEN
ANY CAREER,

360
00:20:13,754 --> 00:20:17,050
NEVER KNOWN DISCOMFORT.

361
00:20:17,050 --> 00:20:20,386
BUT SHE FELT THE CALL OF DUTY.

362
00:20:20,386 --> 00:20:23,639
SHE PLEDGED HER LIFE
TO THE IMPERIAL GUARD.

363
00:20:25,516 --> 00:20:28,769
TALAS COULD HAVE HAD ANYTHING.

364
00:20:28,769 --> 00:20:31,438
ANYONE.

365
00:20:33,399 --> 00:20:35,860
SHE CHOSE ME.

366
00:20:39,363 --> 00:20:41,281
I JUST WANTED YOU TO KNOW.

367
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:53,044
IT'S HER BLOOD.

368
00:20:55,713 --> 00:20:59,383
WHEN A GUARDSMAN
DIES FAR FROM HOME,

369
00:20:59,383 --> 00:21:01,177
HIS COMPANIONS --

370
00:21:03,470 --> 00:21:06,891
<i>HER</i> COMPANIONS --

371
00:21:06,891 --> 00:21:11,353
CARRY A PART OF HER
BACK TO THE ICE

372
00:21:11,353 --> 00:21:13,898
OF ANDORIA.

373
00:21:17,193 --> 00:21:19,528
I WANTED YOU
TO KNOW THAT, TOO...

374
00:21:21,906 --> 00:21:24,617
...BEFORE YOU DIE!

375
00:21:24,617 --> 00:21:26,160
THAT'S ENOUGH!

376
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:28,704
NOT UNTIL HIS BLOOD
PAYS FOR HERS!

377
00:21:28,704 --> 00:21:30,164
KEEP HIM AWAY!

378
00:21:30,164 --> 00:21:32,541
YOU WILL FACE JUSTICE
AT MY HANDS!

379
00:21:32,541 --> 00:21:34,543
THAT'S NOT GONNA
HAPPEN ON MY SHIP.

380
00:21:34,543 --> 00:21:35,836
YES, IT WILL, PINK-SKIN,

381
00:21:35,836 --> 00:21:37,671
BECAUSE IF YOU
AND THE TELLARITES

382
00:21:37,671 --> 00:21:41,134
DON'T SHOW RESPECT
FOR ANDORIAN TRADITION,

383
00:21:41,134 --> 00:21:43,844
THE IMPERIAL GUARD
WILL WITHDRAW ITS SHIPS.

384
00:21:43,844 --> 00:21:45,471
WHAT TRADITION?

385
00:21:45,471 --> 00:21:50,643
UNLESS THIS<i> MURDERER</i>
MEETS ME IN COMBAT,

386
00:21:50,643 --> 00:21:54,230
YOUR PRECIOUS ALLIANCE
IS FINISHED!

387
00:22:01,904 --> 00:22:03,906
I'M RECONNECTING
THE WARP MATRIX!

388
00:22:03,906 --> 00:22:05,866
Shut off the radiation!

389
00:22:05,866 --> 00:22:07,868
WHEN YOU'RE FINISHED.

390
00:22:09,703 --> 00:22:11,664
THERE!

391
00:22:11,664 --> 00:22:15,042
NOW SHUT IT OFF!
AND OPEN THIS HATCH!

392
00:22:20,631 --> 00:22:23,301
COMMANDER, STAY WITH ME.

393
00:22:25,719 --> 00:22:28,806
THE MATRIX HAS
BEEN REACTIVATED.

394
00:22:28,806 --> 00:22:31,349
THEN WE DON'T NEED
THE HUMANS ANYMORE.

395
00:22:33,978 --> 00:22:36,856
WHY DIDN'T YOU LISTEN TO ME?

396
00:22:36,856 --> 00:22:39,608
WE'RE BETTER OFF HERE
THAN ON THE BRIDGE.

397
00:22:39,608 --> 00:22:41,694
[ BEEPING ]

398
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:48,326
TAKE IT TO WARP.
SET A COURSE FOR HOME.

399
00:22:49,535 --> 00:22:51,912
[ ENGINE WHOOSHES ]

400
00:22:51,912 --> 00:22:53,831
WE'RE BACK AT WARP.

401
00:22:53,831 --> 00:22:57,168
I ORDERED YOU
NOT TO HELP THEM.

402
00:22:57,168 --> 00:22:59,962
I APOLOGIZE FOR SAVING
YOUR LIFE, COMMANDER.

403
00:22:59,962 --> 00:23:01,797
IT WON'T HAPPEN AGAIN.

404
00:23:01,797 --> 00:23:03,716
SORRY.

405
00:23:03,716 --> 00:23:05,383
ACCORDING
TO THE BRIDGE SCHEMATIC,

406
00:23:05,383 --> 00:23:06,760
THIS IS AN ACCESS PANEL.

407
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,470
WHERE DOES IT LEAD?

408
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,056
AWAY FROM THE BRIDGE.

409
00:23:10,056 --> 00:23:11,724
WHAT DOES THAT GIVE US?

410
00:23:11,724 --> 00:23:14,185
WE SHOULD ASSUME
THAT WE'RE BEING MONITORED.

411
00:23:15,936 --> 00:23:20,691
DID YOU EVER READ THE MANUAL
THAT CAME WITH THAT THING?

412
00:23:20,691 --> 00:23:23,652
THE WARNING ABOUT
INADVERTENT OVERLOAD.

413
00:23:24,611 --> 00:23:25,905
HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE?

414
00:23:25,905 --> 00:23:28,657
BY NOW, LESS THAN A MINUTE.

415
00:23:31,785 --> 00:23:33,787
[ BEEPING ]

416
00:23:33,787 --> 00:23:35,248
WHAT ACCESS PANEL
ARE THEY TALKING ABOUT?

417
00:23:35,248 --> 00:23:37,083
IT LEADS INTO
THE SUPERSTRUCTURE,

418
00:23:37,083 --> 00:23:39,377
AWAY FROM ANY
CRITICAL EQUIPMENT.

419
00:23:39,377 --> 00:23:41,587
WE'LL DEAL WITH THEM
WHEN THE DRONE RETURNS.

420
00:24:01,899 --> 00:24:03,734
WE'VE GOT TO BE
A SAFE DISTANCE BY NOW.

421
00:24:03,734 --> 00:24:06,362
I WIRED IT DIRECTLY
INTO THE POWER CONDUIT.

422
00:24:28,592 --> 00:24:30,136
WE'VE LOST CONTACT.

423
00:24:37,393 --> 00:24:39,812
THE ANDORIAN TRADITION
SHRAN WANTS TO FOLLOW

424
00:24:39,812 --> 00:24:41,105
IS CALLED THE USHAAN.

425
00:24:41,105 --> 00:24:44,775
BASICALLY,
IT'S A DUEL TO THE DEATH.

426
00:24:44,775 --> 00:24:48,528
THE COMBATANTS
FIGHT WITH THESE.

427
00:24:48,528 --> 00:24:50,739
IT'S CALLED A USHAAN-TOR.

428
00:24:50,739 --> 00:24:52,325
IT'S AN ICE-MINER'S TOOL.

429
00:24:52,325 --> 00:24:55,286
ANDORIANS PLAY
WITH THEM AS CHILDREN.

430
00:24:55,286 --> 00:24:58,038
A TELLARITE WON'T STAND A CHANCE
USING ONE AGAINST SHRAN.

431
00:24:58,038 --> 00:25:00,207
I DON'T THINK
THAT'S GONNA BE AN ISSUE.

432
00:25:00,207 --> 00:25:02,960
AMBASSADOR GRAL'S REFUSING
TO LET NAARG FIGHT.

433
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:06,046
ANDORIANS WILL CONSIDER THAT
A FURTHER INSULT.

434
00:25:07,673 --> 00:25:10,092
WHAT ELSE DO WE KNOW
ABOUT THIS TRADITION?

435
00:25:17,891 --> 00:25:20,394
PLEASE, MAKE YOURSELF AT HOME.

436
00:25:24,690 --> 00:25:29,111
AN OLD FRIEND --
I CARRY IT EVERYWHERE.

437
00:25:32,490 --> 00:25:34,783
TWO HOURS AGO, WE SPOKE
ABOUT A NEW PARTNERSHIP

438
00:25:34,783 --> 00:25:37,870
BETWEEN ANDORIA AND EARTH.

439
00:25:37,870 --> 00:25:39,955
A BENEFIT TO BOTH OUR WORLDS.

440
00:25:39,955 --> 00:25:43,750
YOU'RE THROWING IT AWAY
FOR PERSONAL VENGEANCE.

441
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:47,213
THERE'S MORE TO THIS THAN TALAS.

442
00:25:47,213 --> 00:25:50,632
I LOST MY SHIP,
ALMOST MY ENTIRE CREW.

443
00:25:50,632 --> 00:25:53,052
IF I DO NOTHING TO
AVENGE THESE LOSSES,

444
00:25:53,052 --> 00:25:54,887
WHAT KIND OF A LEADER AM I?

445
00:25:54,887 --> 00:25:57,181
WHY SHOULD ANY SOLDIER
FOLLOW ME AGAIN?

446
00:26:00,309 --> 00:26:03,521
BESIDES, YOU SHOULD
BE WISHING ME LUCK.

447
00:26:05,356 --> 00:26:10,736
I PROVIDE A VOICE FOR YOUR
SPECIES AT THE IMPERIAL GUARD.

448
00:26:10,736 --> 00:26:13,489
I'M VALUABLE TO HUMANS.

449
00:26:16,242 --> 00:26:18,869
I SPOKE TO AMBASSADOR GRAL

450
00:26:18,869 --> 00:26:22,206
ABOUT THE RULES
OF THE USHAAN...

451
00:26:22,206 --> 00:26:26,877
SPECIFICALLY,
THE RIGHT OF SUBSTITUTION.

452
00:26:29,838 --> 00:26:33,884
THE AMBASSADOR'S DECIDED TO
FIGHT IN PLACE OF HIS UNDERLING?

453
00:26:36,887 --> 00:26:38,305
NOT THE AMBASSADOR.

454
00:26:41,392 --> 00:26:42,935
YOU WOULDN'T.

455
00:26:42,935 --> 00:26:45,771
I'M THE SUBSTITUTE.

456
00:26:45,771 --> 00:26:47,814
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO FIGHT ME.

457
00:26:47,814 --> 00:26:50,025
I'M GOING TO HAVE TO KILL YOU.

458
00:26:51,985 --> 00:26:53,820
YOU'RE MY FRIEND.

459
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,655
THEN CALL IT OFF.

460
00:27:01,954 --> 00:27:03,539
I CAN'T.

461
00:27:05,665 --> 00:27:07,793
YOU DID ALL THIS
WITH ONE PHASE PISTOL?

462
00:27:07,793 --> 00:27:10,337
YOU'RE GOOD AT BUILDING THINGS.
I'M GOOD AT BLOWING THEM UP.

463
00:27:10,337 --> 00:27:12,506
I'M THINKING WE SHOULD
GET TO THE OUTER HULL.

464
00:27:12,506 --> 00:27:14,716
NO, WE MIGHT BE SAFER FINDING
ANOTHER AREA WITH LIFE SUPPORT.

465
00:27:14,716 --> 00:27:16,843
THE HULL'S COVERED
WITH SUBSPACE TRANSCEIVERS.

466
00:27:16,843 --> 00:27:18,762
IF I CAN LINK ONE OF THEM
TO OUR COMMUNICATORS,

467
00:27:18,762 --> 00:27:21,265
WE MIGHT BE ABLE TO
CONTACT<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

468
00:27:24,143 --> 00:27:26,644
ADMIRAL, THE DRONE'S
RESTORED CONTACT.

469
00:27:26,644 --> 00:27:28,981
THE REPAIR SYSTEMS
ARE STARTING TO WORK.

470
00:27:28,981 --> 00:27:30,857
IT WILL TAKE DAYS.

471
00:27:30,857 --> 00:27:35,237
LET ME KNOW WHEN IT'S RESTORED
ITS ABILITY TO SELF-DESTRUCT.

472
00:27:35,237 --> 00:27:37,281
-[ DOOR CHIMES ]
-COME IN.

473
00:27:41,868 --> 00:27:43,703
UPDATING YOUR WILL?

474
00:27:43,703 --> 00:27:46,582
YOU EXPECT ME TO LOSE?

475
00:27:46,582 --> 00:27:48,792
SHRAN IS A MEMBER
OF THE IMPERIAL GUARD,

476
00:27:48,792 --> 00:27:51,753
TRAINED IN COMBAT
FROM CHILDHOOD.

477
00:27:51,753 --> 00:27:54,047
HE WON'T BACK DOWN.

478
00:27:54,047 --> 00:27:57,468
HE CAN'T. I UNDERSTAND.

479
00:27:57,468 --> 00:28:00,387
IF YOU BACK DOWN, THE IMPERIAL
GUARD WILL WITHDRAW THEIR SHIPS.

480
00:28:00,387 --> 00:28:04,099
IF I KILL SHRAN, OR ONE
OF THE TELLARITES DOES,

481
00:28:04,099 --> 00:28:07,936
THE ANDORIANS
WILL PULL OUT ANYWAY.

482
00:28:07,936 --> 00:28:09,522
THE TELLARITES
WILL DO THE SAME THING

483
00:28:09,522 --> 00:28:11,565
IF SHRAN KILLS ONE OF THEM.

484
00:28:11,565 --> 00:28:16,820
SO...I'M THE ONLY ONE
WHO CAN BE KILLED,

485
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:19,865
BECAUSE STARFLEET
WON'T WITHDRAW.

486
00:28:23,076 --> 00:28:24,870
THIS OPERATION IS IMPORTANT,

487
00:28:24,870 --> 00:28:29,542
CONSIDERING THAT IT MIGHT LEAD
TO AN ALLIANCE OF PLANETS.

488
00:28:31,251 --> 00:28:33,003
VULCANS HAVE A SAYING --

489
00:28:33,003 --> 00:28:36,340
ONE MAN CAN SUMMON THE FUTURE.

490
00:28:36,340 --> 00:28:38,634
WHAT HAPPENS IF THAT MAN

491
00:28:38,634 --> 00:28:41,178
THROWS AWAY HIS LIFE
BEFORE HIS TIME?

492
00:28:43,013 --> 00:28:46,099
IF I'VE LEARNED ANYTHING THESE
PAST FEW YEARS ON<i> ENTERPRISE,</i>

493
00:28:46,099 --> 00:28:50,979
IT'S THAT THE FUTURE
ISN'T FIXED.

494
00:28:50,979 --> 00:28:53,357
IF ANYTHING HAPPENS TO YOU...

495
00:28:53,357 --> 00:28:56,943
THEN I'D BETTER MAKE SURE
THAT NOTHING DOES.

496
00:29:04,993 --> 00:29:07,705
[ DOOR OPENS ]

497
00:29:09,373 --> 00:29:12,125
DIDN'T EXPECT TO
FIND YOU UP THIS LATE.

498
00:29:12,125 --> 00:29:13,877
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

499
00:29:13,877 --> 00:29:15,504
TOO WIRED TO SLEEP.

500
00:29:15,504 --> 00:29:17,047
HARD TO BELIEVE
THE CAPTAIN'S GONNA BE

501
00:29:17,047 --> 00:29:19,883
FIGHTING A DUEL TO THE DEATH
IN A FEW HOURS.

502
00:29:19,883 --> 00:29:22,344
BARBARIC, IF YOU ASK ME.

503
00:29:22,344 --> 00:29:25,013
-WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?
-THE CODE OF THE USHAAN.

504
00:29:25,013 --> 00:29:26,557
T'POL WANTS ME TO
GO OVER IT AGAIN,

505
00:29:26,557 --> 00:29:28,975
SEE IF I CAN FIND
A WAY OUT OF THIS MESS.

506
00:29:28,975 --> 00:29:30,603
WELL, THE LAST I HEARD,

507
00:29:30,603 --> 00:29:32,438
THE CAPTAIN SOUNDED DETERMINED
TO GO THROUGH WITH IT.

508
00:29:32,438 --> 00:29:34,481
SHE WANTS ME TO FIND
A LOOPHOLE,

509
00:29:34,481 --> 00:29:37,817
SOME WAY TO FORFEIT WITHOUT
OFFENDING THE ANDORIANS.

510
00:29:39,528 --> 00:29:42,531
TWO OF US COULD GET THROUGH
THAT A LOT FASTER.

511
00:29:46,243 --> 00:29:47,661
LOOK AT THIS.

512
00:29:47,661 --> 00:29:50,581
EITHER COMBATANT
CAN POSTPONE A DUEL INDEFINITELY

513
00:29:50,581 --> 00:29:52,916
IF THERE ARE NO CHILDREN
TO CONTINUE HIS CLAN.

514
00:29:52,916 --> 00:29:55,544
HOW DOES THAT HELP US?

515
00:29:55,544 --> 00:29:58,380
AS FAR AS I KNOW, CAPTAIN ARCHER
DOESN'T HAVE ANY KIDS.

516
00:29:58,380 --> 00:30:01,049
IF HE'S KILLED,
HIS CLAN WOULD DIE WITH HIM.

517
00:30:01,049 --> 00:30:05,554
THAT RULE ONLY APPLIES
IF HE'S MARRIED.

518
00:30:05,554 --> 00:30:08,807
DON'T SUPPOSE WE CAN FIND HIM
A WIFE IN THE NEXT FOUR HOURS.

519
00:30:08,807 --> 00:30:10,434
EVEN IF WE COULD,

520
00:30:10,434 --> 00:30:13,186
SOMETHING TELLS ME
THE ANDORIANS WOULD CRY FOUL.

521
00:30:13,186 --> 00:30:15,105
[ SIGHS ]

522
00:30:15,105 --> 00:30:17,399
THERE ARE 12,000 AMENDMENTS
TO THIS RIDICULOUS HONOR CODE.

523
00:30:17,399 --> 00:30:20,819
THERE'S GOT TO BE ONE
THAT CAN GET HIM OUT OF THIS.

524
00:30:20,819 --> 00:30:23,238
INSTEAD OF LOOKING
FOR A LOOPHOLE,

525
00:30:23,238 --> 00:30:24,490
MAYBE WE SHOULD BE TRYING

526
00:30:24,490 --> 00:30:26,866
TO FIND A WAY
FOR THE CAPTAIN TO WIN.

527
00:30:26,866 --> 00:30:29,202
IF THE CAPTAIN WINS,
SHRAN'S DEAD.

528
00:30:29,202 --> 00:30:30,704
THE ALLIANCE FALLS APART.

529
00:30:30,704 --> 00:30:35,167
HAVE YOU EVER BEEN
TO NOBELIA PRIME?

530
00:30:35,167 --> 00:30:37,919
NOT RECENTLY.

531
00:30:37,919 --> 00:30:39,171
THE TRIBAL ELDERS THERE --

532
00:30:39,171 --> 00:30:40,714
THEY CAN
CHALLENGE YOU TO A DUEL

533
00:30:40,714 --> 00:30:42,299
IF YOU LOOK AT THEM
THE WRONG WAY.

534
00:30:42,299 --> 00:30:43,925
HAPPENED TO MY FATHER.

535
00:30:43,925 --> 00:30:45,344
HOW DID HE GET OUT OF IT?

536
00:30:47,095 --> 00:30:50,307
WHICH ONE OF THESE
HAS THE COMBAT RULES?

537
00:30:54,186 --> 00:30:55,979
DON'T TRY AND BLOCK WITH THIS.

538
00:30:55,979 --> 00:30:58,023
WHEN HE SWINGS, INTERCEPT,
DEFLECT, AND HOOK IT AWAY.

539
00:30:58,023 --> 00:31:00,359
BETTER TO INSERT
BETWEEN THE EYES AND TWIST.

540
00:31:00,359 --> 00:31:02,736
ANDORIAN METABOLISM
IS HIGHER THAN HUMANS'.

541
00:31:02,736 --> 00:31:05,489
KEEP MOVING,
YOU'LL EXHAUST HIM.

542
00:31:07,032 --> 00:31:08,992
HOW ABOUT I JUST WIN?

543
00:31:08,992 --> 00:31:10,828
TAKE YOUR PLACES.

544
00:31:15,457 --> 00:31:17,292
THERE IS STILL TIME
TO END THIS.

545
00:31:17,292 --> 00:31:20,045
IT CAN ONLY END ONE WAY.

546
00:31:20,045 --> 00:31:22,047
THIS IS NOT WHAT I WANTED.

547
00:31:22,047 --> 00:31:25,425
THINGS HAVE A WAY OF TURNING OUT
DIFFERENTLY THAN WE EXPECT.

548
00:31:27,219 --> 00:31:29,429
I'M GLAD WE MET.

549
00:31:29,429 --> 00:31:32,974
IN YOUR HONOR, I'LL CONTINUE
TO SUPPORT COOPERATION

550
00:31:32,974 --> 00:31:35,519
BETWEEN THE IMPERIAL GUARD
AND YOUR SPECIES.

551
00:31:36,978 --> 00:31:40,899
LET'S GET THIS OVER WITH.
I GOT A SHIP TO RUN.

552
00:31:48,782 --> 00:31:51,951
I'LL TAKE YOUR BLOOD
TO ANDORIA...

553
00:31:51,951 --> 00:31:54,954
TO THE WALL OF HEROES.

554
00:31:54,954 --> 00:31:56,540
NOT TODAY.

555
00:32:06,216 --> 00:32:07,259
YOU HAVE THE FIRST MOVE.

556
00:32:07,259 --> 00:32:08,510
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

557
00:32:36,204 --> 00:32:37,831
GIVE UP.

558
00:32:37,831 --> 00:32:40,626
A SINGLE STROKE,
AND THERE'LL BE NO PAIN.

559
00:32:40,626 --> 00:32:42,961
YOU THINK I'M LOSING?

560
00:32:42,961 --> 00:32:45,923
I'M JUST TRYING TO MAKE YOU LOOK
GOOD IN FRONT OF YOUR SOLDIERS.

561
00:33:05,317 --> 00:33:06,985
NOW DO YOU GIVE UP?

562
00:33:06,985 --> 00:33:08,528
NEVER!

563
00:33:12,365 --> 00:33:13,951
WRONG CHOICE.

564
00:33:20,206 --> 00:33:22,334
YOU SHOULD HAVE
CUT OFF MY HEAD!

565
00:33:22,334 --> 00:33:26,212
I CONSIDERED IT,
BUT I STILL NEED YOUR HELP.

566
00:33:26,212 --> 00:33:28,131
[ GROANING ]

567
00:33:34,346 --> 00:33:39,184
WHAT GOOD IS A GUARDSMAN
WITHOUT TWO ANTENNAE?

568
00:33:42,103 --> 00:33:43,730
UGH.

569
00:33:43,730 --> 00:33:45,774
YOU'LL BEGIN TO COMPENSATE
WITHIN A DAY OR TWO.

570
00:33:45,774 --> 00:33:48,610
THEY TAKE NINE MONTHS
TO GROW BACK.

571
00:33:48,610 --> 00:33:50,821
IF LEFT UNTREATED.

572
00:33:50,821 --> 00:33:54,032
WITH ELECTRICAL STIMULATION
AND BRISK CRANIAL MASSAGE,

573
00:33:54,032 --> 00:33:56,910
YOU'LL BE BACK TO NORMAL
IN HALF THAT TIME.

574
00:33:56,910 --> 00:34:00,038
I WAS TOLD THAT THE LOSS
OF AN ANTENNA WASN'T CRITICAL...

575
00:34:00,038 --> 00:34:03,000
YOU HUMILIATED ME.

576
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,710
...AND THAT THE USHAAN
IS SETTLED

577
00:34:04,710 --> 00:34:07,337
WHEN ONE FIGHTER IS
RENDERED DEFENSELESS.

578
00:34:09,339 --> 00:34:11,383
ARE WE DONE?

579
00:34:13,510 --> 00:34:16,555
YOU RESPECTED
ANDORIAN TRADITION.

580
00:34:18,264 --> 00:34:19,850
IT'S SETTLED.

581
00:34:19,850 --> 00:34:23,020
-[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]
-Bridge to Captain Archer.

582
00:34:24,771 --> 00:34:29,192
FOUR SHIPS HAVE LOCATED
THE MARAUDER'S POWER SIGNATURE.

583
00:34:29,192 --> 00:34:32,237
CAN YOU PICK UP BIO-SIGNS?

584
00:34:32,237 --> 00:34:35,365
NOT AT THIS DISTANCE.

585
00:34:35,365 --> 00:34:39,327
TRAVIS,
PLOT AN INTERCEPT COURSE.

586
00:34:39,327 --> 00:34:41,538
TAKE US TO MAXIMUM WARP.

587
00:34:41,538 --> 00:34:44,332
INTERCEPT IN 47 MINUTES.

588
00:34:44,332 --> 00:34:46,167
ALERT THE FLEET.

589
00:34:51,256 --> 00:34:53,383
THE DRONE'S SENSORS
HAVE DETECTED<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

590
00:34:53,383 --> 00:34:54,551
IT'S CLOSING.

591
00:34:54,551 --> 00:34:56,887
ACTIVATE THE HOLOGRAPHIC SKIN.

592
00:35:02,308 --> 00:35:04,728
SOMETHING'S STARTING TO DRAW
A LOT OF POWER.

593
00:35:04,728 --> 00:35:07,355
IT'S ALL THE SYSTEMS THAT
WENT DOWN IN THE EXPLOSION.

594
00:35:07,355 --> 00:35:08,815
THEY'RE COMING BACK ONLINE.

595
00:35:08,815 --> 00:35:11,777
-WHAT ABOUT THE WARP MATRIX?
-NOT YET.

596
00:35:11,777 --> 00:35:14,153
BUT IF WE WANT TO CONTACT
<i>ENTERPRISE,</i> WE'D BETTER HURRY.

597
00:35:18,116 --> 00:35:20,410
APPROACHING VISUAL RANGE.

598
00:35:20,410 --> 00:35:23,121
ON SCREEN.

599
00:35:23,121 --> 00:35:25,164
MAGNIFY.

600
00:35:25,164 --> 00:35:26,332
VULCAN?

601
00:35:26,332 --> 00:35:30,045
CHECK THEIR POWER SIGNATURE.

602
00:35:31,546 --> 00:35:33,339
IT DOESN'T MATCH.

603
00:35:33,339 --> 00:35:37,094
TACTICAL ALERT.

604
00:35:37,094 --> 00:35:38,929
CHARGE WEAPONS.

605
00:35:38,929 --> 00:35:43,349
<i>ENTERPRISE</i> WILL REACH THE DRONE
BEFORE THE MATRIX IS RESTORED.

606
00:35:43,349 --> 00:35:45,894
[ DOOR OPENS ]

607
00:35:45,894 --> 00:35:48,939
SENATOR,
I WAS NOT TOLD OF YOUR VISIT.

608
00:35:48,939 --> 00:35:53,652
YOU ALLOWED OUR ENEMIES TO
BOARD AND DISABLE THE DRONE.

609
00:35:54,569 --> 00:35:58,073
I HAVE MY SOURCES, ADMIRAL.

610
00:35:59,783 --> 00:36:03,578
THEN YOU KNOW WE ARE ABOUT
TO ENGAGE THE HUMAN SHIP.

611
00:36:03,578 --> 00:36:07,457
I'M HERE TO WITNESS
ITS DESTRUCTION.

612
00:36:07,457 --> 00:36:08,834
ONE MINUTE.

613
00:36:08,834 --> 00:36:11,044
-[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]
-WE HAVE BIO-SIGNS.

614
00:36:11,044 --> 00:36:12,337
TWO HUMANS.

615
00:36:12,337 --> 00:36:14,172
CAN YOU GET
A TRANSPORTER LOCK?

616
00:36:16,008 --> 00:36:17,759
WE'LL NEED TO BE MUCH CLOSER.

617
00:36:17,759 --> 00:36:21,096
OPEN A CHANNEL.

618
00:36:23,556 --> 00:36:27,310
ARCHER TO TUCKER AND REED.

619
00:36:27,310 --> 00:36:28,979
RESPOND.

620
00:36:31,481 --> 00:36:34,442
We're both here, Captain.

621
00:36:34,442 --> 00:36:35,944
[ SIGHS ]

622
00:36:37,362 --> 00:36:39,156
FIRE.

623
00:36:42,575 --> 00:36:44,327
TARGET ITS WEAPONS.

624
00:36:44,327 --> 00:36:48,040
I CAN'T GET A LOCK
THROUGH THE CAMOUFLAGE.

625
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:51,168
TAKE OUT THE EMITTERS,
BUT DON'T PUNCTURE THE HULL.

626
00:36:58,633 --> 00:37:01,427
[ BOTH GRUNT ]

627
00:37:01,427 --> 00:37:03,055
THEY<i> DO</i> KNOW WE'RE ONBOARD?

628
00:37:03,055 --> 00:37:05,390
THEY'RE PROBABLY TRYING
TO TAKE OUT THE WEAPONS.

629
00:37:05,390 --> 00:37:09,310
<i>ENTERPRISE,</i> ANY CHANCE
OF USING THE TRANSPORTER?

630
00:37:11,354 --> 00:37:13,314
YOU HAVE TO GET CLOSER
TO THE HULL.

631
00:37:13,314 --> 00:37:16,526
-Can you do that?
-WE'RE ON OUR WAY.

632
00:37:16,526 --> 00:37:18,570
WE'VE LOST THE EMITTERS.

633
00:37:18,570 --> 00:37:20,197
WARP STATUS?

634
00:37:20,197 --> 00:37:23,533
TWO MINUTES.
MORE ENEMY SHIPS ARE CLOSING.

635
00:37:23,533 --> 00:37:25,785
IF<i> ENTERPRISE</i> STOPS
THE SELF-REPAIR SEQUENCE --

636
00:37:25,785 --> 00:37:28,914
THE DRONE WILL ESCAPE.

637
00:37:35,879 --> 00:37:38,798
<i>ENTERPRISE!</i>
WE'RE AT THE HULL!

638
00:37:45,055 --> 00:37:48,058
THE SHIP'S MOVEMENT IS TOO
ERRATIC. I CAN'T GET A LOCK.

639
00:37:48,058 --> 00:37:49,935
THEY'RE TARGETING
OUR WARP CORE.

640
00:37:49,935 --> 00:37:52,229
HULL PLATING IS AT 43%.

641
00:37:52,229 --> 00:37:53,980
36%.

642
00:37:53,980 --> 00:37:57,025
SHUT DOWN WEAPONS.
ALL POWER TO HULL PLATING.

643
00:37:57,025 --> 00:37:59,861
TRAVIS, BRING US ABOUT.

644
00:37:59,861 --> 00:38:02,739
TRIP, MALCOLM,
WE CAN MAKE ONE MORE PASS.

645
00:38:02,739 --> 00:38:04,991
GET THE HELL OUT OF THERE.

646
00:38:04,991 --> 00:38:08,453
THEIR WEAPONS ARE OFFLINE.
THEY'RE VULNERABLE.

647
00:38:11,873 --> 00:38:15,710
I CAN'T IMAGINE HOW THINGS
COULD GET MUCH WORSE!

648
00:38:15,710 --> 00:38:17,503
I CAN.

649
00:38:17,503 --> 00:38:18,964
AAH!

650
00:38:23,635 --> 00:38:25,262
THEY'RE CLEAR.

651
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:31,643
SENSORS ARE DOWN.

652
00:38:31,643 --> 00:38:34,020
I'VE LOST THEM.

653
00:38:37,983 --> 00:38:40,443
SIX MORE ENEMY SHIPS
WITHIN RANGE.

654
00:38:40,443 --> 00:38:42,779
20 SECONDS TO WARP.

655
00:38:42,779 --> 00:38:44,656
WE'VE GOT COMPANY --
ALLIANCE SHIPS.

656
00:38:44,656 --> 00:38:45,949
TELL THEM NOT TO FIRE.

657
00:38:45,949 --> 00:38:47,826
OUR PEOPLE ARE OUT THERE.

658
00:38:56,709 --> 00:38:58,253
THE MATRIX IS RESTORED.

659
00:38:58,253 --> 00:38:59,378
WITHDRAW.

660
00:39:15,603 --> 00:39:19,482
THEY LEFT US.
YOU WERE RIGHT.

661
00:39:19,482 --> 00:39:20,984
THIS IS WORSE.

662
00:39:20,984 --> 00:39:23,069
Anyone out there need a lift?

663
00:39:33,746 --> 00:39:36,624
IF I HAD TO WEAR THIS HELMET
FOR ONE MORE MINUTE,

664
00:39:36,624 --> 00:39:38,668
I SWEAR IT WOULD'VE
FUSED TO MY SKULL.

665
00:39:38,668 --> 00:39:40,837
[ CHUCKLES ]

666
00:39:40,837 --> 00:39:42,839
I TELL YOU, I'D LIKE TO FIND
THE DESIGNER OF THIS SUIT

667
00:39:42,839 --> 00:39:45,133
AND MAKE HIM
WEAR IT FOR THREE DAYS.

668
00:39:45,133 --> 00:39:46,759
YEAH.

669
00:39:46,759 --> 00:39:48,345
THANKS FOR WHAT
YOU DID BACK THERE.

670
00:39:48,345 --> 00:39:49,971
YEAH, YOU WOULD HAVE DONE
THE SAME FOR ME.

671
00:39:49,971 --> 00:39:53,016
NO, YOU TOOK A BIG CHANCE...

672
00:39:53,016 --> 00:39:55,852
WHICH MAKES WHAT I HAVE TO DO
ALL THE MORE DIFFICULT.

673
00:39:57,687 --> 00:40:00,273
I'M PUTTING YOU ON REPORT.

674
00:40:00,273 --> 00:40:02,817
YOU'RE WHAT?

675
00:40:02,817 --> 00:40:04,694
YOU DISOBEYED
A DIRECT ORDER.

676
00:40:04,694 --> 00:40:07,655
I SAVED YOUR LIFE!

677
00:40:07,655 --> 00:40:09,824
IF YOU PUT A REPRIMAND
IN MY FILE,

678
00:40:09,824 --> 00:40:12,785
IT COULD BE YEARS BEFORE
I'M EVEN ELIGIBLE FOR...

679
00:40:12,785 --> 00:40:14,704
[ LAUGHING ]

680
00:40:16,789 --> 00:40:18,208
ARE YOU PULLING MY LEG?

681
00:40:18,208 --> 00:40:22,628
M-MALCOLM, YOU'RE JUST
SUCH AN EASY TARGET.

682
00:40:22,628 --> 00:40:24,714
[ LAUGHING ]

683
00:40:29,969 --> 00:40:32,138
[ DOOR OPENS ]

684
00:40:36,768 --> 00:40:38,228
THE MARAUDER GOT AWAY.

685
00:40:40,730 --> 00:40:43,024
ONE OF THE TELLARITE SHIPS
WAS HIT.

686
00:40:43,024 --> 00:40:46,694
AN ANDORIAN WARSHIP
RESCUED THE CREW.

687
00:40:46,694 --> 00:40:49,697
SO IT'S STILL OUT THERE --

688
00:40:49,697 --> 00:40:52,284
AS YOU SAID,
A COMMON THREAT.

689
00:40:52,284 --> 00:40:55,870
I BELIEVE WE HAVE MORE TO
DISCUSS THAN TRADE DISPUTES.

690
00:41:04,254 --> 00:41:06,631
WHY WAIT UNTIL
WE GET TO BABEL?

691
00:41:31,739 --> 00:41:35,034
THE DRONE HAS
REENTERED ROMULAN SPACE.

